gov.nasa.jpf.vm

Interface SchedulerFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ContextBoundingSchedulerFactory, DefaultSchedulerFactory, DistributedSchedulerFactory, PrioritySchedulerFactory

    public interface SchedulerFactory
    interface of factory object that creates all ChoiceGenerators required to implement scheduling strategies
